{"tid":2116927,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"後日放榜，小心教育傳銷騙子","createTime":"2020-07-20T12:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T09:21:30.000Z","uid":315470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f82596bba99a65a2a23ff7fa36383118a6077d","tid":2116927,"uid":315470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"放榜之後會有好多陌生人打電話比你，毒撚都可能有靚女關心"},{"pid":"1e8d2d49a67ca2d635708e69db412bc01c19c0bc","tid":2116927,"uid":315470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:01:14.000Z","msg":"可能會有人打電話比你讀唔讀IELTS同叫你讀完全無認證到課程，報讀任何課程唔該先上網打該教育機構的名。例如環球專上書院 傳銷/呃人等等，睇下人地評語"},{"pid":"5103e3afbfb6425705a33809d4ce85d165239bb1","tid":2116927,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0531c2315a8f51f18ada3da4e45a807aca7deae5","tid":2116927,"uid":7828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span class=\"green\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=a1805bfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=52829d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=5bd05146\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"917d854e0a9e84fcbaf29ae1252baeaf2b2bac31","tid":2116927,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"UP"},{"pid":"6e586a6770527825ca109fba10a186943eed62ff","tid":2116927,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T17:05:29.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"0861acbf7530b9151793c2a8e24874bb05bd0b7d","tid":2116927,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"UP"}]}